      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the sophisticated buyer. Demonstrating consistent mechanical reliability and a well-preserved interior, the automobile has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our dealership's exacting standards for performance and safety. It offers a refined driving experience and remains a testament to diligent previous ownership. This is an exemplary acquisition for those who demand quality and long-term value in a pre-owned executive vehicle.",
      "price": 34500.0,
