      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Silver Grey Metallic, a driver\u2019s specimen that balances raw performance with mechanical integrity. Under the hood, the S54B32 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of atmospheric induction, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential for precise torque vectoring. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its 'good' classification, the chassis remains taut with upgraded poly-bushings and refreshed dampers. The interior maintains its driver-centric ergonomics with Nappa leather bolsters showing light wear but no structural failure. A mechanically sorted icon ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
